its of habitable\nexomoons. If either planet hosted a satellite at a distance greater than 10\nplanetary radii, then this could indicate the presence of a habitable moon.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 24 Sep 2012 16:31:28 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 4 Feb 2013 15:32:50 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 30 Oct 2013 19:07:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-10-31"}
