aling of $L_z$, and the reversal of the ground-state angular momentum for a\ntoroidal geometry, would provide a signature of broken time-reversal symmetry\nof the ground state of superfluid \\Hea, as well as direct observation of chiral\nedge currents.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 25 Sep 2012 05:58:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-09-26"}
